hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 在八面体场中，$d^2$（高自旋）的CFSE为
$$CFSE_o=2\bigl(-\tfrac{2}{5}\Delta_o\bigr)=-\tfrac{4}{5}\Delta_o.$$
2. 在四面体场中，$d^2$（高自旋）的CFSE为
$$CFSE_t=2\bigl(-\tfrac{3}{5}\Delta_t\bigr)=-\tfrac{6}{5}\Delta_t.$$
3. 分裂能的关系为
$$\Delta_t=\tfrac{4}{9}\Delta_o.$$
4. 比值为
$$\frac{CFSE_o}{CFSE_t}
=\frac{-\tfrac{4}{5}\Delta_o}{-\tfrac{6}{5}\Delta_t}
=\frac{\tfrac{4}{5}}{\tfrac{6}{5}}\frac{\Delta_o}{\Delta_t}
=\frac{4}{6}\,\frac{\Delta_o}{\Delta_t}
=\frac{2}{3}\cdot\frac{\Delta_o}{\Delta_t}
=\frac{2}{3}\cdot\frac{9}{4}
=\frac{3}{2}.$$
